### Constructor Chaining

1. **Non-argument constructor behavior:**  
   Jab aap ek non-argument constructor banate hain, to jab bhi is class ki subclass run hoti hai, parent ka non-argument constructor automatically call hota hai, chahe aap usko explicitly call karein ya na karein. 

   ```java
   public ClassName() {                    
       // some statements            
   }

   public ClassName() {
       super();
       // some statements
   }
